The paper deals with error correction codes for multimedia streaming applications, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the transmission of packets over a channel, which falls under networked and internet systems (cs.NI). The paper proposes a new model for packet erasure channels, which involves statistical inference (cs.SI) and data structures (cs.DS).
